blog.description: Hey. I'm a broken 17 year old. Stuff I like: Marvel, Rick and Morty, Stranger Things, P!ATD, FOB (my favorite band ever), lofi music, Black Mirror, video games, Jacksepticeye, CoryxKenshin, John Wolfe and so much more. I am a girl (she/her). Heteroromantic asexual. I’ve been diagnosed with depression and generalized anxiety disorder. I have disordered eating habits. I have an overactive imagination which is a blessing and a curse. I like to make stories. Oh, and I'm a loner so I'll be on here often. Feel free to message me!
